## Next Steps (For Deployment)

To complete the Speed Insights setup on Vercel:
1. Enable Speed Insights in your Vercel project dashboard
2. Deploy the project to Vercel
3. After deployment, Speed Insights will automatically begin collecting performance metrics
4. View metrics in the Vercel dashboard under "Speed Insights"

